-> output devise:
    -> Lsmod
        - (ifo about kernel modules)
    -> Lspci
        - (info about PCI devices)
    -> Lspcmcia
        - (info about PCMCIA devices)
    -> Lsusb
        - (info about USB bus)
    -> Lshal
        - (HAL devices base) delete in new linux's
    -> Lshw
        - (detail info about parts)

-> utils for kernel modules control:
    -> Lsmod
        - (ifo about kernel modules)
    -> Modinfo {module name}
        - (module info)
    -> Rmmod {module name}
        - (delete kernel module)
    -> insmod {module name}
        - (install kernel module)
    -> Modprobe {module name}
        - (delicate delete or add modules)